text: thumbZuzanna Smykała (born 10 January 1990 in Chorzów)Polish 2018 Olympic team at the Polish Olympic Committee websiteAthlete Profile Zuzanna Smykala Olympic.org is a Polish snowboarder. She competed for Poland in the snowboard cross at the 2018 Winter Olympics, finishing 23rd in qualifying and fifth in Heat 4, eliminating her from the competition.Results - Ladies' Snowboard Cross Quarterfinal 4 Olympic.org Smykała had previously finished seventh in the snowboard cross at the 2015 Winter Universiade. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Olympic snowboarders of Poland Category:Snowboarders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Polish female snowboarders Category:Living people Category:People from Chorzów Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Poland Category:Universiade medalists in snowboarding Category:Competitors at the 2015 Winter Universiade
